MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-1310. Williamson v. Walles.

Lucas App. No. L-08-1010, 2008-Ohio-3847. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
